{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/87245", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/87245/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/87245/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/87245/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/87245", "id": 946971198, "node_id": "MDU6SXNzdWU5NDY5NzExOTg=", "number": 87245, "title": "Type inference for the `!` type behaves unexpectedly", "user": {"login": "IQBigBang", "id": 19934663, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjE5OTM0NjYz", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/19934663?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/IQBigBang", "html_url": "https://github.com/IQBigBang", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/IQBigBang/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/IQBigBang/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/IQBigBang/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/IQBigBang/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/IQBigBang/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/IQBigBang/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/IQBigBang/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/IQBigBang/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/IQBigBang/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [{"id": 650731663, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWw2NTA3MzE2NjM=", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/labels/C-bug", "name": "C-bug", "color": "f5f1fd", "default": false, "description": "Category: This is a bug."}], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 3, "created_at": "2021-07-18T07:20:15Z", "updated_at": "2021-07-18T14:52:32Z", "closed_at": "2021-07-18T14:52:32Z", "author_association": "NONE", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "In summary, for the following code:\r\n\r\n```rust\r\nfn ok() {\r\n    let x: *const ! = std::ptr::null();\r\n    let m = unsafe { &*x };\r\n    println!(\"{}\", m);\r\n}\r\n\r\nfn wrong() {\r\n    let x: *const (!, u8) = std::ptr::null();\r\n    let m = unsafe { (&*x).0 };\r\n    println!(\"{}\", m);\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nThe first function compiles (and then obviously fails at runtime), but the second one doesn't compile and produces the following message:\r\n\r\n```\r\nerror[E0277]: `()` doesn't implement `std::fmt::Display`\r\n  --> src/main.rs:12:20\r\n```\r\n\r\nWhich is wrong, because the type of `m` should be `!`.\r\n\r\nAdding any sort of type constraints, such as the following, makes the code pass the type-checker:\r\n```rust\r\nfn foo() {\r\n    let x: *const (!, u8) = std::ptr::null();\r\n    let m: ! = unsafe { (&*x).0 };\r\n    println!(\"{}\", m);\r\n}\r\n\r\n// Or\r\n\r\nfn bar() {\r\n    let x: *const (!, u8) = std::ptr::null();\r\n    let m = unsafe { (&*x).0 };\r\n    f(m);\r\n    println!(\"{}\", m);\r\n}\r\n\r\nfn f(_: !) {}\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Meta\r\n`rustc --version --verbose`:\r\n```\r\nrustc 1.55.0-nightly (c7331d65b 2021-07-17)\r\nbinary: rustc\r\ncommit-hash: c7331d65bdbab1187f5a9b8f5b918248678ebdb9\r\ncommit-date: 2021-07-17\r\nhost: x86_64-pc-windows-msvc\r\nrelease: 1.55.0-nightly\r\nLLVM version: 12.0.1\r\n```\r\n", "closed_by": {"login": "jyn514", "id": 23638587, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjIzNjM4NTg3", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/23638587?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/jyn514", "html_url": "https://github.com/jyn514", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jyn514/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jyn514/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jyn514/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jyn514/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_